##chapter Multithreading
##section Intro

#p
Burning provides threads implementation built on a tom of boreaux-threads (and reimplements its features for
some implementatoins.
#-

#p Currently supported implementations (fully):
   #list 
     clozurecl
     sbcl
#-

Support of clisp is also possible, but current version (2.49) has bug in #term{exemption exemptions} implementation,
so it doesn't pass our tests,
#-

#p
Other implementations, supported by bordeaux-threads, a possible supported too, but we don't tested library on them.
#-

##-section
##-chapter